Nollywood actor, Uche Maduagwu has accused singer, Davido of only using the name of the mother of his son, Chioma Rowland to drive the sales of tickets for his upcoming show in The O2 Arena, London.
He made this claim on Wednesday, a day after Davido praised Chioma’s cooking on social media.
Maduagwu said, “So all these months you ignore this good woman for no reason on social media, all of a sudden when 02 Arena TICKET no dey sell like Odogwu own you miraculously remember say she be world greatest chef on social media? Just to get Nigerians in the UK to fill seats for your show or what exactly? This is just so wrong bro, I love your music but if you promise woman marriage and for no reason no fulfil that promise after introduction, engagement ring and belle, no dey take am promote or grow your music career then.”
Davido and Chioma share a son, Ifeanyi.
 
